+## Folder Readability Polish
+
+- Created rollback archive:
+  `Docs/Design/FolderReadabilityArchive/2026-05-04-before-folder-readability/`
+- Kept the current colorful folder cards, but made folder names easier to scan
+  with a shared title component, calmer title weight, stricter two-line breaks,
+  fixed title-block alignment, and slightly smaller icon badges.
+- Applied the same folder title treatment to Home folder tiles and the full
+  Folders grid so one-line and two-line names feel intentionally aligned.
